- [x] **资源约束定义** - $\forall r \in \mathcal{R}: \text{usage}(r) \leq \text{limit}(r)$
- [x] **内存安全映射** - $\forall p \in \text{Pointers}: \text{valid}(p) \land \text{accessible}(p)$
